tore_item_assets/steam/apps/1941420/extras/1b4ebec3113591e9539fa4cafd7aad64.webp?t=1707792470\" width=600 height=63 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Eat Burritos</strong> - Shove as many delicious burritos into Bear’s mouth as possible!<br></li><li><strong>Power Ups</strong> - Consume and interact with a wild variety of juiced-up power-ups to aid (or inhibit) Bear in their stinky journey for maximum fullness!<br></li><li><strong>Customize Bear</strong> - Collect numerous outfits, accessories, and tools to completely deck out Bear; some of which can be used to get and edge up on falling garbage!<br></li><li><strong>Traverse Multiple Areas</strong> - Using special warp burritos, Bear can fart out massive wormholes to send them across space and time to other lands!<br></li><li><strong>Different Modes</strong> - Play through three different modes: Story, Arcade, and Endless!<br></li><li><strong>Online Leaderboards</strong> - Climb the ranks and become Top Bear!<br></li><li><strong>Original Soundtrack</strong> - Jam out to bunch of funky jams created by D Fast!</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941420/extras/e7d8e55cc05db0f114df1fb78b304bc0.poster.avif?t=1707792470\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941420/extras/e7d8e55cc05db0f114df1fb78b304bc0.webm?t=1707792470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941420/extras/e7d8e55cc05db0f114df1fb78b304bc0.mp4?t=1707792470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
